main: ^On your way to Glasgow International Dining Hall, you hear some suspicious noises coming from the trash.
^On further inspection, it turns out to be just Oski rummaging through the bins.
^He notices you and excitedly waves you down.
^HEY COME HERE COME LOOK AT WHAT I FOUND

b: ^Trembling with hesitation, you meander your way over to the center of the trash bins where Oski jumps up and down, waiting for you.
^Oski then pulls out the largest beaver you've ever seen in your life and holds it from the beak like those fishing dads with their fish.
